---
import DefaultLayout from '../../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'Document Digitization Services in India | Tyrus Technologies';
---

<DefaultLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description="Document digitization services in India. We plan your project, scan your files, do quality checks, and deliver structured digital archives so your team can find records easily."
>
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-700">
        Services · Digitization
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        End‑to‑end document digitization services.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-700">
        We design and run complete digitization projects from planning and indexing design to on‑site
        or offsite scanning, quality checks and delivery of structured digital archives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr,1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Project coverage.</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• Site survey and estimation of page volumes.</li>
          <li>• Indexing and folder structure design with your teams.</li>
          <li>• On‑site or offsite scanning setup based on sensitivity and space.</li>
          <li>• Multi‑level image and index quality checks.</li>
          <li>• Creation of searchable digital archives and meta‑data.</li>
          <li>• Secure hand‑back or storage of physical files.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Best suited for</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• Multi‑year hospital MRD archives.</li>
          <li>• Centralized KYC, loan and account files.</li>
          <li>• Government department and land record archives.</li>
          <li>• Legal case records and contract repositories.</li>
          <li>• Corporate record rooms and carton storage.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How a digitization project runs.</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>We study your current records, volumes and access patterns.</li>
          <li>We define batching, indexing rules and naming standards.</li>
          <li>We deploy a trained team on‑site or move files to a secure facility.</li>
          <li>We scan, index and verify documents batch by batch.</li>
          <li>We share periodic MIS so you can track project progress.</li>
          <li>We deliver final digital archives and help connect them to your systems.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-6 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Benefits for your organization</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• Clear visibility into which records are already digitized.</li>
          <li>• Faster document retrieval for operations, audits and legal needs.</li>
          <li>• Reduced physical storage and better use of office space.</li>
          <li>• Lower risk of lost, damaged or misplaced documents.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/10 via-sky-500/10 to-slate-100 p-8 ring-1 ring-emerald-200">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Start planning your digitization roadmap.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          Tell us about your volumes, locations and timelines. We will share a practical project plan
          and budget range based on similar work we have delivered.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/#cost-calculator"
            class="rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-emerald-500/40 hover:bg-emerald-700"
          >
            Get a free estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50"
          >
            Talk to a specialist
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

